  (see also $ASTROMAKE/make/README)

First time install:

CVS:
    cvs -d :pserver:guest@cvs.astro.umd.edu:/home/cvsroot login
    (password: guest)
    cvs -d :pserver:guest@cvs.astro.umd.edu:/home/cvsroot co astromake
    cd astromake
    ./configure
    make install
    source astromake_start
    

TARFILE:

    cd /usr/local/astro/make
    make install


Upgrades:

    astromake all astromake


Typical installations

    astromake all pgplot miriad karma



-- 

Cheating:

 *  in opt you can symlink to 'astromake' packages that live someplace else.
    usually you have to brand a status file in status/package_name
